external libs needed for ALT package

 libs to download
  glfw-2.7.8  
    1) download from http://sourceforge.net/projects/glfw/
    2) make x11
    3) copy glfw-2.7.8/include/GL  to  inc/
    4) copy glfw-2.7.8/lib/x11/libglfw.*  to lib/  or change location in makefile

  
  Ceres-solver 1.6.0
    1) download http://ceres-solver.googlecode.com/files/ceres-solver-1.6.0.tar.gz
    2) compile and install on system
    3) copy headers to inc/ceres or change location in makefile

  CVXOPT 1.1.5
    Fedora: install from repo: python-cvxopt.x86_64    

other libs from repos
 Ubuntu:
  libx11-dev
  libxext-dev
  libxfixes-dev
  mesa-libGLU-devel
 
 Fedora 
  libx11-dev
  libxext-dev
  libxfixes-dev
  libglu1-mesa-dev
